title: Cannabase's Beck: Growing Online Marijuana Marketplace (Audio)

description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Jennifer Beck, Co-Founder and Managing Director of Cannabase, on creating an online wholesale marijuana marketplace that connects commercial growers with retailers and dispensaries.
